item.title: About Me
item.description: I am an iOS developer. I have also spent my time on a number of other projects: A Programming Language An OpenGL Renderer An Evolutionary Optimizer based on NSGA-II A Runtime Reflection library for Swift based off the ABI A JSON Parser in Swift A simple software based nueral network I run Brisbane Cocoaheads I also work for Tappr on our iOS Point of Sale app
